// SCRIPT_ID: UNIFIED_HMM_MAIN
// STOP VALIDITY FIX - December 2024
// CHANGES:
// 1. Removed all 1-penny clamp code (math.min/max with 0.01)
// 2. Added minimum stop distance validation (15% of ATR)
// 3. VWAP stops validated for correct side AND minimum distance
// 4. Swing stops validated for minimum distance
// 5. Invalid stops fallback to ATR with "ATR-Fallback" label
// 6. evaluateBestStop returns -1 for invalid stops (shown as "invalid" in table)
// 7. Chart Stats table now shows live Open P&L and Position data


